Introduction

Kim Tae Rae is a South Korean singer under Wakeone Entertainment. In 2023, he participated in the hit survival show, "Boys Planet," where he ranked 6th place, allowing him to become a member of ZEROBASEONE.

He made his official debut as a member of ZEROBASEONE on July 10, 2023, with the mini album "Youth in the Shade."
